app - airPhoto! [1.0]
Download now from iTunes! With airPhoto! you can share your photos in your iPhone / iPod touch 2nd generation wirelessly with other iPhone / iPod touch running iPhone OS 3.0 or above. System Requirements Supported devices: a) iPhone 3Gb) iPhone 3GSc) iPod Touch 2nd GenerationiPhone OS 3.0 or above Notes * Please note that airPhoto! requires iPhone 3G or iPod touch 2nd Generation and above running iPhone OS 3.0 or above. * airPhoto! makes use of Bluetooth capabilities in iPhone OS 3.0. However, iPhone OS 3.0 does not currently support file sharing with other Bluetooth enabled devices. * To ensure maximum compatibility, please verify that the other user is running the same version of airPhoto! as you. * Bluetooth is a registered Trademark of Bluetooth SIG, Inc. 1. Push the "Connect" button. 2. Follow the instructions on the screen. Click on the "Accept" button. 3. Push the "Send" button. 4. Select the photo you wish to send. 5. The photo you selected will be transmitted to the other iPhone / iPod touch 2nd Generation Download now from iTunes!
